Nora Fatehi is a Canadian-Moroccan actress, dancer, and model who primarily works in the Indian film industry. Nora gained popularity in India through her appearances in various dance reality shows, including "Jhalak Dikhhla Jaa" and "Bigg Boss." Her breakthrough came in 2018 when she appeared in the music video for the song "Dilbar" from the film "Satyameva Jayate." Her dance performance in the song garnered immense attention and made her a household name in India. Nora has since featured in several successful Bollywood films, including "Street Dancer 3D," "Bharat," and "Batla House."
